message.body: I live! I don't know if I'll make it out tonight. I would love to but will have to play it by ear. Will let you know if I plan to join. Hope you're well!
Good to hear from you!! Turns out the party tonight is guest list only, but if you're free before 6:30 or after 8:30, let's get a drink! And let's hang out soon either way.
